config BR2_PACKAGE_RISCV_TESTS
    bool "riscv-tests"
    depends on BR2_TOOLCHAIN_EXTERNAL
    help
      Unit tests for RISC-V processors.
      Requires a multilib toolchain, which builds all ABIs for 32-bit and 64-bit.
      E.g., ilp32, ilp32d, etc. The included buildroot toolchain does not support this, neither for 32-bit nor 64-bit.
      Therefore, an external toolchain would be required which enables multilib, e.g., https://github.com/riscv-collab/riscv-gnu-toolchain
